Protest action by taxi associations in Pietermaritzburg’s CBD has resulted in all major routes being closed off. The following roads have been affected: Ohrtman Rd, Dr Chota Motala, R33/R103/R56/M70, Chatterton Rd, Boshoff Street, Boom Street and Greyling Street. Motorists have been asked to avoid all these routes. A motorist told TabloidNewsKZN that people are unable to get into or out of the town. “There is complete chaos,” said the motorist.